description: Locations, events, or actions related to the preposition "on"
Prepositions related to location or position
The common pattern activating this neuron involves descriptions of items located on a surface or an object impacting/influencing/affecting another object.
Prepositions, especially "on", in contexts related to location, status, or topic of discussion
The preposition "on" occurs frequently, often related to dates, topics of discussion or consideration, locations, and online platforms
